    <div class="content"><p>I sincerely hope that love has absolutely NOTHING to do with their inability to conceive.  It was the one aspect of the show that I despised.  I remember when they first mentioned it I groaned audibly.  My theories involve a more logical explanation, one I mentioned earlier, which seems to not be true, however, with the revelation that Ellen believes in love being a factor.  Perhaps the Kobolians were responsible for it then, I don't know.</p>
</div>
