    <div class="content"><p>I was just trying to roughly describe the posting, not summarize it, as it is just above.  My point was he was saying you can&#8217;t read much from the glasses and I am saying you can&#8217;t read much from text so small it won&#8217;t be visible even in HDTV.</p>
